# Packer templates for FreeBSD 10.4-RC1

Templates to create Vagrant boxes for FreeBSD 10.4-RC1 (amd64 and i386).


## Prerequisites

* [Packer][] v0.8.6+
* [Vagrant][] v1.7.2+
* [VirtualBox][]
