	* Version 4.3.28+ for Mac OS X (You may want to stay with 4.3.28 which allows [HAXM][] to work in parallel.)
* [VMware][] Workstation v11.1.0+ / VMware Fusion v8.0+
* [ESXi][] (vSphere Hypervisor) v5.5+

